#Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},${misc:Depends}
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: HCC2 is an experimental compiler for OpenMP 4.5 using
 LLVM 6.0 for offloading to either Radeon GPUs or Nvidia GPUs. 
 HCC2 requires either libamdgpu or cuda or both.
 Dependencies are not specified here for flexibility. 
